name: Summer Slices Fragrance Lamp Oil
description: Fresh from the garden cucumber perfectly blended with juicy honeydew slices. A fresh, sweet fragrance reminiscent of sunny summer days.  16 oz bottle.

Includes heavy decorative shade, snuffer cap, regular size wick, funnel & instructions.  Measures 6.5 inches.  Makes a great gift!
